title: Estimated number of World of Warcraft subscribers 2015 to 2023
summary: This is a line chart with an x axis representing Year and a y axis representing Subscribers in millions, containing a total of 9 data points.
In general Subscribers in millions has fallen over the Year.
Subscribers in millions is slightly decreasing from 2015 to 2023.
The most drastic decrease took place within the Year 2016 and 2017.
The highest Subscribers in millions, of value 5.67 was reached at Year 2016
The lowest Subscribers in millions, of value 4.46 was reported at Year 2023
